{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "29dfe8a3-f973-4ca2-9120-c26ba5256d96",
		"name": "YourFinAdvisor E2E Chat Flow with AI",
		"description": "A collection to test the full lifecycle of the chat API including AI assistant responses, file uploads, and chat favorites functionality.\n\n**Important Notes:**\n\n1. Run the '0. Authenticate and Get Token' request first to set the JWT for all other requests.\n    \n2. File upload tests (0a-0e) require you to manually select files in Postman. These tests verify authentication, single/multiple file uploads, and error handling.\n    \n3. Favorites tests (1c-1f) demonstrate marking/unmarking chats as favorites and verifying the sorting behavior.\n    \n4. For test '3b. Wait and check for AI response' - The auto_reply runs in background, so you may need to manually wait 3-5 seconds before running this test, or run it twice.\n    \n5. SSE tests (6, 6c) will show raw event data in Postman. For proper streaming experience, use a browser or SSE client.\n    \n\n**New Favorites Feature:**\n\n- Chats can be marked as favorites with automatic ranking\n    \n- Favorites appear at the top of chat lists, sorted by rank (highest/newest first)\n    \n- Non-favorites are sorted by date after favorites",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "45986761",
		"_collection_link": "https://finadvisordev.postman.co/workspace/finadvisorDEV-Workspace~1a449275-63e6-4295-8f75-f96030eee41a/collection/26433417-29dfe8a3-f973-4ca2-9120-c26ba5256d96?action=share&source=collection_link&creator=45986761"
	},
